mqvpn (0.6.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add configurable TUN MTU via --mtu CLI flag and INI/JSON config; cap
    server per-client MTU notification to actual TUN MTU (#131, #132).
  * Add --cc flag for congestion control selection (bbr2, bbr, cubic, none).
  * Add wlb_udp_pin scheduler support (#140).
  * Add routes management option (#143).
  * Fix failover storm crash and add dynamic path budget expansion.
  * Fix always reconnect on path_id=0 removal; fix double-rotation.
  * Fix xqc_conn_close_path() failure when removing path_id=0.
  * Fix path add/remove race.
  * Fix JSON MTU upper bound to match INI parser (65535 → 9000).
  * Raise max_path_id_grant_max_value from 64 to 128; bump xquic submodule
    for reciprocal MAX_PATH_ID fix.

